  "body": "### Describe the feature\n\nChai released a new breaking version, and the [current docs](https://www.npmjs.com/package/@nomicfoundation/hardhat-chai-matchers) do not specify which version you need to install.\r\n\r\nWith this version, compilation does not work and gives a HH19 error\r\n`Error HH19: Your project is an ESM project (you have \"type\": \"module\" set in your package.json) but your Hardhat config file uses the .js extension.`\r\n\r\nIt would be beneficial to support the latest version of the testing library\n\n### Search terms\n\nchai chai5 hardhat-chai-matchers",
