    "author_association": "COLLABORATOR",
    "body": "Hi @Mantas-M, Hardhat version 2.x with TypeScript does not support ESM packages. If you're interested in trying `chai@5`, you can enable the experimental ESM support as described in this thread: [Hardhat Issue #3385](https://github.com/NomicFoundation/hardhat/issues/3385#issuecomment-1841380253). Otherwise, for compatibility with your current setup, you should install `chai@4`, following the installation instructions in the documentation you referenced.\r\n",
